(229, 'Baked in Brooklyn (2016)', '2017/07/film-baked-in-brooklyn-2016.jpg', '', 'RXN5SzhwcFVFVkZOampyTEtJQWV2S1MxM0hVTUhCRTBERTBZeHN6djFHYz0=', '&lt;p&gt;A recent college graduate (Brener) decides to sell marijuana on the streets of Manhattan after losing his job at a consulting firm. He soon meets the girl of his dreams (Daddario). With an &amp;#8230;&lt;br /&gt;Rory Rooney&lt;br /&gt;Todd Bartels, Evangelo Bousis, Josh Brener, Harold Bridgeforth&lt;br /&gt;14 Oct 2016 ()&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Comedy', 'Rory Rooney', 'Evangelo Bousis, Harold Bridgeforth, Josh Brener, Todd Bartels', '', 'BluRay', '5.4', '1 jam 40 menit', '2016-10-14'),
(230, 'Before I Wake (2016)', '2017/07/film-before-i-wake-2016.jpg', '', 'N0Z3VFI1bndyNTQ0TUgwMHU1Q09BdVQxQk85Y0VZUlVsUk01bmE2SjlPVT0=', '&lt;p&gt;In this intense and heart pounding supernatural thriller, Jessie (Kate Bosworth) and Mark (Thomas Jane) decide to take in a sweet and loving 8-year-old boy, Cody. Unbeknownst to them, Cody is terrified of falling asleep. At first, they assume his previous unstable homes caused his aversion to sleep, but soon discover why: Cody&amp;#8217;s dreams manifest in reality as he sleeps. In one moment they experience the incredible wonder of Cody&amp;#8217;s imagination, and in the next, the horrific nature of his night terrors. To save their new family, Jessie and Mark embark on a dangerous hunt to uncover the truth behind Cody&amp;#8217;s nightmares.&lt;br /&gt;Mike Flanagan&lt;br /&gt;Annabeth Gish, Kate Bosworth, Jacob Tremblay, Thomas Jane&lt;br /&gt;07 Apr 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Dream, Insomnia, Orphan Boy, Nightmares', 'Drama, Fantasy, Horror', 'Mike Flanagan', 'Annabeth Gish, Jacob Tremblay, Kate Bosworth, Thomas Jane', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.1', '1 jam 40 menit', '2016-04-07'),
