(302, 'Brooklyn (2015)', '2017/07/film-brooklyn-2015.jpg', '', 'dkJ3MUFneEcyMlljTDcwdEhzRmV3M0xMd0doK0xRVnlidlprRFhHem5WZz0=', '', '', 'Drama, Romance', 'John Crowley', 'Brid Brennan, Hugh Gormley, Jim Broadbent, Saoirse Ronan', 'Canada, Ireland, Uk', 'BluRay', '7.5', '1 jam 51 menit', '2015-11-04'),
(303, 'Blue Jay (2016)', '2017/07/film-blue-jay-2016.jpg', '', 'OFQxRnJhK2IxL3BmSjRsUndTUXJhUExscHVsN0E2SWdVOHNUaVpBUndQaz0=', '&lt;p&gt;The two main characters, Jim and Amanda (Mark and Sarah) were high school sweethearts, but as time has passed they moved on with their lives and they have now become adults who have had their own different experiences along the way and now that they have reunited, we find they still have that chemistry between them. This was great casting, these two actors work really well together, normally I throw 9&amp;#8217;s and 10&amp;#8217;s all over the place These characters are so natural, so done with this earth in the sense that they live in our world, they are believable and now need an escape even if it is just for a single day. This movie focuses on just them, these two people for the entire film and I cannot thank Mark Duplass for this (he is the screenwriter) because I have not seen a film where the two main characters are the only characters, I didn&amp;#8217;t get sick of them, I did not find them boring, ever, they were very fleshed out and they felt like genuine, real people who were put in this situation and now find out that they work really well together.&lt;br /&gt;Alex Lehmann&lt;br /&gt;Mark Duplass, Sarah Paulson, Clu Gulager, James Andrews&lt;br /&gt;07 Oct 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;1 nomination.&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Drama', 'Alex Lehmann', 'Clu Gulager, James Andrews, Mark Duplass, Sarah Paulson', 'Usa', 'WEBDL', '7.3', '1 jam 20 menit', '2016-10-07'),
(304, 'Born to Be Blue (2015)', '2017/07/film-born-to-be-blue-2015.jpg', '', 'YWRWRE1hcmlENG81UVp5aWZMNGIyY0Rua1BFL05TUCtPY3B4Y0VJTlNlYz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Film ini akan berfokus pada cerita Chet Baker. Dia adalah seorang pemain terompet yang juga sekaligus sebagai penyanyi, yang setelah menjadi ikon musik jazz pada era tahun 1950an, juga tak kalah terkenalnya sebagai pengguna narkoba. Mengambil cerita kehidupannya di akhir tahun 1960an, Born to Be Blue adalah sebuah kisah cinta yang mencampurkan beberapa fakta bersejarah dan fiksional yang digabungkan menjadi gambaran kehidupan tak biasa Chet Baker.&lt;br /&gt;Pada tahun 1966 seorang bernama Chet Baker (Ethan Hawke) yang mana menerima kunjungan di saat masih berada dipenjara oleh seorang sutradara dengan maksud membuat film tentang kisah hidupnya ketika Baker mulai mencoba narkoba. Dikemudian hari di Los Angeles proses syuting dilaksanakan yang mana Baker mengajak seorang wanita yang tak lain adalah pacarnya bernama Jane (Carmen Ejogo) agar mau tampil di film tersebut. Namun suatu hari Baker mendapatkan penyerangan dari orang lain yang tak dikenalinya dengan menyebabkan gigi bagian depannya rusak dan bibirnya mengalami cidera sehingga membawanya terancam tidak bisa memainkan terompet lagi.&lt;br /&gt;Robert Budreau&lt;br /&gt;Ethan Hawke, Carmen Ejogo, Callum Rennie, Tony Nappo&lt;br /&gt;13 Sep 2015 (UK, Canada, USA)&lt;br /&gt;3 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Jazz, Biography, Historical Figure', 'Biography, Drama, Music', 'Robert Budreau', 'Callum Rennie, Carmen Ejogo, Ethan Hawke, Tony Nappo', 'Canada, Uk, Usa', 'BluRay', '6.9', '1 jam 37 menit', '2015-09-13'),
