(566, 'Doubutsu Sentai Zyuohger the Movie: The Heart Pounding Circus Panic (2016)', '2017/07/film-doubutsu-sentai-zyuohger-the-movie-the-heart-pounding-circus-panic-2016.jpg', '', 'L0tETGQwQ0czbkdXdE0zWnJISG5neHdMMVd5WFJiK3pQT3U4TElFMjMxST0=', '&lt;p&gt;Sirkus Luar Angkasa tiba di bumi, dan pemimpin mereka, Domidol, bermaksud memperbudak semua Zyumans sebagai bagian dari rencananya untukmenciptakan kembali seluruh alam semesta menjadi arena sirkus. Tapi yang menghalanginya adalah Zyuohgers, yang berniat melindungi planet ini darinya.&lt;br /&gt;Takayuki Shibasaki&lt;br /&gt;Masaki Nakao, Miki Yanagi, Sh&ocirc;hei Namba, Tsurugi Watanabe&lt;br /&gt;06 Aug 2016 (Japan)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Tokusatsu, Super Sentai, Zyuohger', 'Action, Short', 'Takayuki Shibasaki', 'Masaki Nakao, Miki Yanagi, ShÃƒÂ´hei Namba, Tsurugi Watanabe', 'Japan', 'DVDRip', '7.4', '0 jam 27 menit', '2016-08-06'),
(567, 'From the Land of the Moon (2016)', '2017/07/film-from-the-land-of-the-moon-2016.jpg', '', 'M0w0V1Bta3p5SlZ4MDdKeDVZSWVTWXhjUXNUcTBXOFVNcUNEZTNnUkxYcz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Gabrielle (Marion Cotillard) comes from a small village in the South of France, at a time when her dream of true love is considered scandalous, and even a sign of insanity. Her parents marry her to Jos&eacute; (Alex Brendem&uuml;hl), an honest and loving Spanish farm worker who they think will make a respectable woman of her. Despite Jos&eacute;&amp;#8217;s devotion to her, Gabrielle vows that she will never love Jos&eacute; and lives like a prisoner bound by the constraints of conventional post-World War II society until the day she is sent away to a cure in the Alps to heal her kidney stones. There she meets Andr&eacute; Sauvage (Louis Garrel), a dashing injured veteran of the Indochinese War, who rekindles the passion buried inside her. She promises they will run away together, and Andr&eacute; seems to share her desire. Will anyone dare rob her of her right to follow her dreams?&lt;br /&gt;Nicole Garcia&lt;br /&gt;Marion Cotillard, Louis Garrel, Alex Brendem&uuml;hl, Brigitte Ro&uuml;an&lt;br /&gt;19 Oct 2016 (France, Belgium, Canada)&lt;br /&gt;13 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Based On Novel, Female Protagonist, Post World War Ii, Woman Director', 'Drama, Romance', 'Nicole Garcia', 'Alex BrendemÃƒÂ¼hl, Brigitte RoÃƒÂ¼an, Louis Garrel, Marion Cotillard', 'Belgium, Canada, France', 'BluRay', '6.7', '2 jam 0 menit', '2016-10-19'),
(568, 'Eddie the Eagle (2016)', '2017/07/film-eddie-eagle-2016.jpg', '', 'UEpIU1ExVXdlSkdIalljaUhlUEE3eUl6dGJVNDFnSWc0RUFWUGhGb21iQT0=', '&lt;p&gt;Inspired by true events, Eddie the Eagle is a feel-good story about Michael &amp;#8220;Eddie&amp;#8221; Edwards (Taron Egerton), an unlikely but courageous British ski-jumper who never stopped believing in himself &amp;#8211; even as an entire nation was counting him out. With the help of a rebellious and charismatic coach (played by Hugh Jackman), Eddie takes on the establishment and wins the hearts of sports fans around the world by making an improbable and historic showing at the 1988 Calgary Winter Olympics. From producers of Kingsman: The Secret Service, Eddie the Eagle stars Taron Egerton as Eddie, the loveable underdog with a never say die attitude.&lt;br /&gt;Dexter Fletcher&lt;br /&gt;Tom Costello, Jo Hartley, Keith Allen, Dickon Tolson&lt;br /&gt;26 Feb 2016 (UK, USA, Germany)&lt;br /&gt;1 win.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Underdog, Ski Jump, Biography, Sport, Britain, Olympics, Skiing, True Story', 'Biography, Comedy, Drama', 'Dexter Fletcher', 'Dickon Tolson, Jo Hartley, Keith Allen, Tom Costello', 'Germany, Uk, Usa', 'BluRay', '7.4', '1 jam 45 menit', '2016-02-26'),
(569, 'From Vegas to Macau III (2016)', '2017/07/film-from-vegas-to-macau-iii-2016.jpg', '', 'cTR0OEhqZWl5TXlEUjhFOGpuUUpQV0w2YUpyZ2dxaCtGNS9SbTEzTGxhaz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Ken is holding a wedding ceremony in Macau for her daughter, Rainbow, who is marrying his protege, Vincent. Ken&amp;#8217;s best buddies, Vic and Mark, are invited to the wedding. On the wedding day itself, Mark receives a phone call from Michael Chen, who warns him that a mysterious tycoon has hired mercenaries to assassinate Ken. The wedding is then sabotaged, while Ken and Mark are accused to have engulfed DOA&amp;#8217;s illicit money. Once again, Ken and Mark are being chased by assassins and Michael arrives to rescue the guys along with the help of Faye, Ko Chun&amp;#8217;s niece.&lt;br /&gt;Jing Wong&lt;br /&gt;Sally Victoria Benson, Jacky Cheung, Nick Cheung, David Chiang&lt;br /&gt;05 Feb 2016 (China, Hong Kong)&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Comedy, Drama', 'Jing Wong', 'David Chiang, Jacky Cheung, Nick Cheung, Sally Victoria Benson', 'China, Hong Kong', 'BluRay', '1.9', '1 jam 52 menit', '2016-02-05'),
