(778, 'How to Plan an Orgy in a Small Town (2015)', '2017/07/film-how-to-plan-an-orgy-in-a-small-town-2015.jpg', '', 'ZU5kWlJNaGRJMEpZNFczODQvMWhvdFE0d05IeXNVOUpad29CeWtjMkNzWT0=', '&lt;p&gt;How to Plan an Orgy in a Small Town is about a group of friends who live in the picturesque town of Beaver&amp;#8217;s Ridge-the epitome of wholesomeness and strong family values. Their orderly life is interrupted by the homecoming of Cassie Cranston, whom they slut-shamed into leaving town when she was a teenager.&nbsp;Now a big-city sex writer, Cassie returns home to face an unwelcome reception by her former friends, and finds an opportunity to seek revenge by writing a book about them when they ask her if she&amp;#8217;ll help them plan an orgy.&lt;br /&gt;Jeremy LaLonde&lt;br /&gt;Jewel Staite, Ennis Esmer, Lauren Lee Smith, Katharine Isabelle&lt;br /&gt;19 Sep 2015 (Canada)&lt;br /&gt;3 wins.&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Comedy', 'Jeremy LaLonde', 'Ennis Esmer, Jewel Staite, Katharine Isabelle, Lauren Lee Smith', 'Canada', 'BluRay', '5.5', '1 jam 41 menit', '2015-09-19'),
