(790, 'Go Lala Go 2 (2015)', '2017/07/film-go-lala-go-2-2015.jpg', '', 'c2dac29teEI2cjZMSEJ5U1JreG5ReldFanpJQjhOUE41UnJET0p5bjVMbz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Lala starts a new career in a new position after company restructures. She encounters a handsome and successful client, Chen Feng, who proposed to Lala, and broke up with Wang Wei. Lala is in a dilemma between love and career.&lt;br /&gt;Andrew Chien&lt;br /&gt;Ariel Lin, Vic Chou, Bo-lin Chen, Michelle Chen&lt;br /&gt;11 Nov 2015 (Taiwan)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Fianc&eacute;, Career Woman, Wedding, Fianc&eacute; Fianc&eacute;e Relationship, Fianc&eacute;e', 'Comedy, Romance', 'Andrew Chien', 'Ariel Lin, Bo-lin Chen, Michelle Chen, Vic Chou', 'Taiwan', 'BluRay', '5.3', '1 jam 41 menit', '2015-11-11'),
