(799, 'Hostile Border (2015)', '2017/07/film-hostile-border-2015.jpg', '', 'TmlDaHorYkVPdUdMdHRvRllVaENUQWtyVEQyaWYzUjhpd1VPZmtXTC9Uaz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Raised in the U.S., Claudia (22) is an undocumented illegal immigrant living beyond her means in a twisted version of the American dream. When she&amp;#8217;s arrested by the FBI for credit card fraud, Claudia is quickly deported to Mexico. Speaking no Spanish and lost in her foreign &amp;#8220;homeland,&amp;#8221; she reluctantly takes refuge at her estranged father&amp;#8217;s cattle ranch. As she clashes with her unyielding father, her attempts to return to the U.S. thrust her into a dangerous bond with a foreign smuggler, Ricky. Caught between her father&amp;#8217;s sermons, Ricky&amp;#8217;s promises, and the encroaching military, Claudia must navigate a tightrope of impossible choices.&lt;br /&gt;Michael Dwyer&lt;br /&gt;Veronica Sixtos, Julio Cedillo, Roberto Urbina, Jorge A. Jimenez&lt;br /&gt;16 Apr 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;3 wins &amp;#038; 1 nomination.&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Drama', 'Michael Dwyer', 'Jorge A. Jimenez, Julio Cedillo, Roberto Urbina, Veronica Sixtos', 'Usa', 'HDRip', '5.3', '1 jam 28 menit', '2015-04-16'),
(800, 'Goat (2016)', '2017/07/film-goat-2016.jpg', '', 'YmNWdVcveVoyNUtadjRTRWNxNEdROWZKWTUzeG1HN0wzdHZxL05UREMrUT0=', '&lt;p&gt;Reeling from a terrifying assault, a 19 year-old enrolls into college with his brother and pledges the same fraternity. What happens there, in the name of &amp;#8220;brotherhood,&amp;#8221; tests him and his loyalty to his brother in brutal ways.&lt;br /&gt;Andrew Neel&lt;br /&gt;Ben Schnetzer, Nick Jonas, Gus Halper, Danny Flaherty&lt;br /&gt;23 Sep 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;3 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Brother Brother Relationship, College, Based On True Story, Hazing, Student, Bare Chested Male, Fraternity', 'Drama', 'Andrew Neel', 'Ben Schnetzer, Danny Flaherty, Gus Halper, Nick Jonas', 'Usa', 'WEBDL', '5.8', '1 jam 42 menit', '2016-09-23'),
(801, 'Home (2015)', '2017/07/film-home-2015.jpg', '', 'QmhjTFRSQ1RoTHR6YzhLTkpDSGFnY0paRkZ1VWg1VHpZSENCNHNaengrbz0=', '&lt;p&gt;When Oh, a loveable misfit from another planet, lands on Earth and finds himself on the run from his own people, he forms an unlikely friendship with an adventurous girl named Tip who is on a quest of her own. Through a series of comic adventures with Tip, Oh comes to understand that being different and making mistakes is all part of being human. And while he changes her planet and she changes his world, they discover the true meaning of the word HOME.&lt;br /&gt;Tim Johnson&lt;br /&gt;Jim Parsons, Rihanna, Steve Martin, Jennifer Lopez&lt;br /&gt;27 Mar 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;4 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Friendship, Spaceship, Space, Alien, Alien Friendship', 'Adventure, Animation, Comedy', 'Tim Johnson', 'Jennifer Lopez, Jim Parsons, Rihanna, Steve Martin', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.7', '1 jam 34 menit', '2015-03-27'),
(802, 'Gods of Egypt (2016)', '2017/07/film-gods-egypt-2016.jpg', '', 'NEx4WDRzSy9lbDdtUERUYnE2djBKU3ZqS254NEJ0RW40clF3aGhRbVVyTT0=', '&lt;p&gt;Set, the merciless god of darkness, has taken over the throne of Egypt and plunged the once peaceful and prosperous empire into chaos and conflict. Few dare to rebel against him. A young thief, whose love was taken captive by the god, seeks to dethrone and defeat Set with the aid of the powerful god Horus.&lt;br /&gt;Alex Proyas&lt;br /&gt;Brenton Thwaites, John Samaha, Courtney Eaton, Nikolaj Coster-Waldau&lt;br /&gt;25 Feb 2016 (USA, Australia)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Egypt, Fight, Nile, Sand, War, Thief, Rescue, Gods, Egyptian Mythology, Dessert, Egyptian', 'Action, Adventure, Fantasy', 'Alex Proyas', 'Brenton Thwaites, Courtney Eaton, John Samaha, Nikolaj Coster-Waldau', 'Australia, Usa', 'BluRay', '5.5', '1 jam 40 menit', '2016-02-25'),
(803, 'High &amp;amp; Low the Red Rain (2016)', '2017/07/film-high-low-the-red-rain-2016.jpg', '', 'NmFaRmlYWS9LTHRlTURCYktLVTFReFVvdnNMb1RqWm10SnZZamtMNEc4Zz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Film HIGH &amp;#038; LOW THE RED RAIN merupakan kelanjutan dari bagian pertama seri film HIGH &amp;#038; LOW yang dibintangi oleh para performer anggota EXILE TRIBE. The Amamiya Brothers yang terdiri dari Masaki dan Hiroto terus melacak keberadaan Takeru, kakak mereka yang menghilang satu tahun sebelumnya. Ketiganya telah bersama terus sejak kecil, sehingga Masaki dan Hiroto berharap Takeru akan muncul saat peringatan kematian orang tua mereka. Namun, di hari yang dinantikan, bukan Takeru yang muncul.&lt;br /&gt;Yudai Yamaguchi&lt;br /&gt;Onodera Akihara, No&eacute;mie Nakai, Takumi Sait&ocirc;, Takahiro&lt;br /&gt;08 Oct 2016 (Japan)&lt;br /&gt;', '', '', 'Yudai Yamaguchi', 'NoÃƒÂ©mie Nakai, Onodera Akihara, Takahiro, Takumi SaitÃƒÂ´', 'Japan', 'BluRay', '7.5', '1 jam 40 menit', '2016-10-08'),
(804, 'Hunter&amp;#039;s Prayer (2017)', '2017/07/film-hunters-prayer-2017.jpg', '', 'MXdKbkxZZmQzZGdkNEd4SCtPQjZ0RFRsT1pnaisvUGNYMGhFdU1NUVl3bz0=', '&lt;p&gt;This high octane thriller focuses on Lucas, (Sam Worthington), a solitary assassin, hired to kill a young woman, Ella, (Odeya Rush). When he can&amp;#8217;t bring himself to pull the trigger the plan falls apart, setting in motion a twisted game of cat and mouse. Now both are marked for death and forced to form an uneasy alliance. Relentlessly pursued across Europe, their only hope for survival is to expose those responsible for brutally murdering her family and bring them to justice.&lt;br /&gt;Jonathan Mostow&lt;br /&gt;Sam Worthington, Odeya Rush, Allen Leech, Amy Landecker&lt;br /&gt;09 Jun 2017 (Germany)&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Action, Thriller', 'Jonathan Mostow', 'Allen Leech, Amy Landecker, Odeya Rush, Sam Worthington', 'Germany', 'WEBDL', '', '1 jam 31 menit', '2017-06-09'),
