(834, 'Ghosthunters on Icy Trails (2015)', '2017/07/film-ghosthunters-icy-trails-2015.jpg', '', 'eXVkN2dXSG1ES1pXcmpqVDc1K3llak9zMEVtQzYrdjdFWlMxYUVIclc2QT0=', '&lt;p&gt;They couldn&amp;#8217;t be more different, the members of the trio that allies in the fight against an Ancient Ice Ghost (AIG): Tom, an easily scared boy, Hetty, a professional ghosthunter and the &amp;#8230;&lt;br /&gt;Tobi Baumann&lt;br /&gt;Anke Engelke, Milo Parker, Bastian Pastewka, Karoline Herfurth&lt;br /&gt;02 Apr 2015 (Germany, Austria, Ireland)&lt;br /&gt;2 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Comedy, Family, Fantasy', 'Tobi Baumann', 'Anke Engelke, Bastian Pastewka, Karoline Herfurth, Milo Parker', 'Austria, Germany, Ireland', 'BluRay', '5.5', '1 jam 39 menit', '2015-04-02'),
(835, 'It Happened One Valentine&amp;#039;s (2017)', '2017/07/film-it-happened-one-valentines-2017.jpg', '', 'dUp1enlVOVpXQTJKK3pUeGUwaVEvVEx0TzdXUkVGeGRDVHN5VGJvS3o2RT0=', '&lt;p&gt;When ambitious reporter Allie Rusch is recruited by vindictive music manager Vivian Cartwright to play cupid to famous pop musicians Caleb Greene and Carson Peet in return for an exclusive story over Valentine&amp;#8217;s weekend, Allie soon realizes Caleb has his sights set on her. Now, torn between her big career move and her growing feelings for Caleb, Allie is left to question whether she can coerce Caleb into something his heart does not desire, or if she should fall in love and make him her very own Valentine.&lt;br /&gt;Jake Helgren&lt;br /&gt;James Maslow, Haley Webb, Brittany Underwood, Tommy Savas&lt;br /&gt;07 Feb 2017 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Comedy, Romance', 'Jake Helgren', 'Brittany Underwood, Haley Webb, James Maslow, Tommy Savas', 'Usa', 'WEBDL', '5.4', '1 jam 30 menit', '2017-02-07'),
