(837, 'Goodnight Mommy (2015)', '2017/07/film-goodnight-mommy-2015.jpg', '', 'eEU2TlNHdlFGajk1NUlEbEgxR0FyOVNWRXh5bEQrdmRGZS92bGFUbFlJdz0=', '', '', 'Drama, Mystery, Thriller', 'Severin Fiala, Veronika Franz', 'Elias Schwarz, Hans Escher, Lukas Schwarz, Susanne Wuest', 'Austria', 'BluRay', '6.7', '1 jam 40 menit', '2015-09-11'),
(838, 'It Watches (2016)', '2017/07/film-it-watches-2016.jpg', '', 'dHo3S2tlVkpvRE51bWR1dkVPZTZGb0ZGL3JDVFVWQjl1eG9nN05lUWU5Yz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Andre, recovering from a recent accident, agrees to help his friend Robert by taking over a house sitting job at an unusual home nestled in the heart of ColdWater Canyon. As the day turns &amp;#8230;&lt;br /&gt;Dave Parker&lt;br /&gt;Ivan Djurovic, Rick Irwin, Sanny van Heteren, James Duval&lt;br /&gt;06 Dec 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Isolation, House', 'Thriller', 'Dave Parker', 'Ivan Djurovic, James Duval, Rick Irwin, Sanny van Heteren', 'Usa', 'WEBDL', '3.8', '1 jam 26 menit', '2016-12-06'),
(839, 'Jack of the Red Hearts (2015)', '2017/07/film-jack-of-the-red-hearts-2015.jpg', '', 'dWxiWFBzNDNJc2grYUFUTUpjVjAwSEVHeGhCYUEvMEQ0VUM5REtENEtXST0=', '&lt;p&gt;A streetwise teenage runaway is on the lam from her probation officer. Her name is Jacquelyn, but if you call her anything but Jack, she&amp;#8217;ll cut you. Needing to lay low, earn money, and gain adequate stability to rescue her 11-year-old sister Coke from foster care, Jack cons her way into a suburban home as live-in helper for their autistic 11-year-old daughter, Glory. Much to her surprise, Jack has a unique ability to connect with the nonverbal little girl. As she positively impacts Glory, the family impacts Jack. Particularly Kay, Glory&amp;#8217;s mother. As these two scrappy survivors find an affinity with each other, Kay finds in Jack a daughter she can talk to. When romantic sparks fly between Jack and Robert, Glory&amp;#8217;s 17-year-old brother, we see a group of wounded people poignantly and surprisingly begin to heal each other-just a little bit. But the law catches up, the truth comes out, and Jack is forced to make a choice-to save her own hide, or save someone else.&lt;br /&gt;Janet Grillo&lt;br /&gt;AnnaSophia Robb, Famke Janssen, Scott Cohen, Israel Broussard&lt;br /&gt;06 May 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;2 wins.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Woman Director', 'Drama, Family', 'Janet Grillo', 'AnnaSophia Robb, Famke Janssen, Israel Broussard, Scott Cohen', 'Usa', 'HDRip', '7.2', '1 jam 42 menit', '2015-05-06'),
(840, 'Ithaca (2015)', '2017/07/film-ithaca-2015.jpg', '', 'T2hxVGpQdzhqaE1UZUV4QmZreHh4NlQzbHdSc3FRSkxwd2RubVl4YlJJQT0=', '&lt;p&gt;Fourteen-year-old Homer Macauley is determined to be the best and fastest bicycle telegraph messenger anyone has ever seen. His older brother has gone to war, leaving Homer to look after his widowed mother, his older sister and his 4-year-old brother, Ulysses. And so it is that as spring turns to summer, 1942, Homer Macauley delivers messages of love, hope, pain&amp;#8230; and death&amp;#8230; to the good people of Ithaca. And Homer Macauley will grapple with one message that will change him forever. Based on Pulitzer Prize-winning author William Saroyan&amp;#8217;s 1943 novel, The Human Comedy, ITHACA is a coming-of-age story about the exuberance of youth, the abruptness of change, the sweetness of life, the sting of death, and the sheer goodness that lives in each and every one of us.&lt;br /&gt;Meg Ryan&lt;br /&gt;Tom Hanks, Meg Ryan, Jack Quaid, Sam Shepard&lt;br /&gt;29 Oct 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;1 nomination.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Based On Novel', 'Drama', 'Meg Ryan', 'Jack Quaid, Meg Ryan, Sam Shepard, Tom Hanks', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '5.6', '1 jam 36 menit', '2015-10-29'),
(841, 'Into the Grizzly Maze (2015)', '2017/07/film-into-the-grizzly-maze-2015.jpg', '', 'QStDMVRPRUpxbGtaaUlvSTJrSmRXdHJDMkhSZUl5SEp4c2lhbFhQd2xHYz0=', '', '', 'Action, Horror, Thriller', 'David Hackl', 'Billy Bob Thornton, James Marsden, Piper Perabo, Thomas Jane', 'Canada, Usa', 'BluRay', '5.3', '1 jam 34 menit', '2015-08-13'),
(842, 'Into the Forest (2015)', '2017/07/film-into-the-forest-2016.jpg', '', 'N3B2K2tPM1FpcVBkakJrRFk3ZkRjdGc3eHd4ZFkrUDNITTJJM1ljVUVIST0=', '&lt;p&gt;In a world that is increasingly dependent on electricity, a power outage seems like an awful predicament. Mankind is using electricity for the past 140 years, but still, we can&amp;#8217;t imagine ourselves living in a world deprived of electricity. In such a difficult and dreary situation found themselves a father and his two daughters, after a seemingly normal power outage lingered on, changing the lives of everyone in the region. What was the reason for this outage? Is it regional, or does it affect the whole country? No one really knows and as time passes, the family will have to put to the test its survival skills, adaptability and endurance, but most of all, the integrity of the familial bonds.&lt;br /&gt;Patricia Rozema&lt;br /&gt;Ellen Page, Evan Rachel Wood, Max Minghella, Callum Rennie&lt;br /&gt;03 Jun 2016 (Canada)&lt;br /&gt;1 win &amp;#038; 3 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Female Nudity, Rape, Fire, Dancer, Based On Novel, Baby, Sister Sister Relationship, Nudity, Dystopia, Rifle, Death Of Father, Survival, Forest, Chainsaw, Pregnancy, Power Outage, Childbirth, Woman Director, Wild Pig, Leak', 'Drama, Sci-fi', 'Patricia Rozema', 'Callum Rennie, Ellen Page, Evan Rachel Wood, Max Minghella', 'Canada', 'BluRay', '5.9', '1 jam 41 menit', '2016-06-03');
