(1216, 'Our Brand Is Crisis (2015)', '2017/07/film-our-brand-is-crisis-2015.jpg', '', 'UnA2aWE2NFMzbUw2R3RCWjhHbzFjMUVXUVl1elJPZ3ZiSHRVWnBDc0FxWT0=', '&lt;p&gt;In 2002, Bolivian politician Pedro Gallo hires American James Carville&amp;#8217;s political consulting firm, Greenberg Carville Shrum, to help him win the 2002 Bolivian presidential election. GCS brings in Jane Bodine to manage the campaign in Bolivia. Battling her arch nemesis, the opposition&amp;#8217;s political consultant Pat Candy, Bodine successfully uses American political campaign strategies to lead Gallo to victory against Victor Rivera.&lt;br /&gt;David Gordon Green&lt;br /&gt;Sandra Bullock, Billy Bob Thornton, Anthony Mackie, Joaquim de Almeida&lt;br /&gt;11 Sep 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;1 nomination.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Political Campaign, South America', 'Comedy, Drama', 'David Gordon Green', 'Anthony Mackie, Billy Bob Thornton, Joaquim de Almeida, Sandra Bullock', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.1', '1 jam 48 menit', '2015-09-11'),
(1217, 'No Escape (2015)', '2017/07/film-no-escape-2015.jpg', '', 'N3NRcWJEN3MzODdyNnVoMHdtY0ZNMTA5cXBubW83WCtFUnY3aXlLL0Mxaz0=', '&lt;p&gt;When Jack (Owen Wilson) finds an opportunity to move to Southeast Asia to head his water manufacturing company&amp;#8217;s new plant there, he immediately jumps at the opportunity and moves his family there. When they get there; they seem to be having problems, the electronics don&amp;#8217;t work and rarely any cars are seen in the streets. When he goes to the market the next morning, he finds himself caught in the middle of a violent rebellion headed by armed rebels executing foreigners. Jack must get back to the hotel and with the help of a mysterious British &amp;#8220;tourist&amp;#8221; (Pierce Brosnan), must get his family to the American Embassy in the midst of the chaos. But is there any escape?&lt;br /&gt;John Erick Dowdle&lt;br /&gt;Lake Bell, Pierce Brosnan, Sterling Jerins, Owen Wilson&lt;br /&gt;26 Aug 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Coup, American, Family, Foreign', 'Action, Thriller', 'John Erick Dowdle', 'Lake Bell, Owen Wilson, Pierce Brosnan, Sterling Jerins', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.8', '1 jam 43 menit', '2015-08-26'),
