(1747, 'The Hunger Games: Mockingjay - Part 2 (2015)', '2017/07/film-the-hunger-games-mockingjay-part-2-2015.jpg', '', 'QlZudDZuR3prT0ZvcStYZ0lhNUF1Q1FmYWFKeHNOWWhQWk1EVWJNMWxPND0=', '&lt;p&gt;After young Katniss Everdeen agrees to be the symbol of rebellion, the Mockingjay, she tries to return Peeta to his normal state, tries to get to the Capitol, and tries to deal with the battles coming her way&amp;#8230;but all for her main goal; assassinating President Snow and returning peace to the Districts of Panem. As her squad starts to get smaller and smaller, will she make it to the Capitol? Will she get revenge on Snow? Or will her target change? Will she be with her &amp;#8220;Star-Crossed Lover&amp;#8221;, Peeta? Or her long time friend, Gale? Deaths, Bombs, Bows and Arrows, A Love Triangle, Hope. What will happen?&lt;br /&gt;Francis Lawrence&lt;br /&gt;Jennifer Lawrence, Josh Hutcherson, Liam Hemsworth, Woody Harrelson&lt;br /&gt;18 Nov 2015 (USA, Germany)&lt;br /&gt;5 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Revolution, Dystopia, Game Of Death, 3d, Mockingjay, Hunger Games, Strong Female Lead', 'Adventure, Sci-fi', 'Francis Lawrence', 'Jennifer Lawrence, Josh Hutcherson, Liam Hemsworth, Woody Harrelson', 'Germany, Usa', 'BluRay', '6.6', '2 jam 16 menit', '2015-11-18'),
(1748, 'The Horde (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-horde-2016.jpg', '', 'ZmFjOHIxb0NxVC81VXBiOUNURU9RTW5xTk1ydmRZYXV3S3B3TEFDUXNOTT0=', '&lt;p&gt;The film follows John Crenshaw as he accompanies his girlfriend and her students on a weekend nature-photography expedition deep into the woods. What should be an educational and fun-filled weekend turns into horror as the group is besieged by an unspeakable evil &amp;#8211; a horde of hideously disfigured, mutated humans with an insatiable taste for blood. As things go from bad to worse, Crenshaw becomes their only hope if they are going to get out alive.&lt;br /&gt;Jared Cohn&lt;br /&gt;Matthew Willig, Bill Moseley, Vernon Wells, Costas Mandylor&lt;br /&gt;06 May 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Martial Arts', 'Action, Horror', 'Jared Cohn', 'Bill Moseley, Costas Mandylor, Matthew Willig, Vernon Wells', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '4.1', '1 jam 28 menit', '2016-05-06'),
(1749, 'The Hunt (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-hunt-2016.jpg', '', 'S3NwQm9Jb1BNWnZza1NnY0pIOVFoTk50MWVwR0FIYjdCVXo3cWNKeWZ2az0=', '&lt;p&gt;Ki-Sung is suffering from the aftereffects of a coal mine incident. Now he goes to the mountain everyday to hunt for a living. But on this particular day, he sees a suspicious group of hunters and chases them. The group is lead by the business-man Park who has found a claim of gold at the mountain-site. But while trying to buy the area from the old woman who owns it, they got into an argument and Park kills her furiously. Ki-Sung tried to stop them, but now they are after him to erase the only witness of their crime. The beginning of a brutal fight for survival.&lt;br /&gt;Lee Woo-Chul&lt;br /&gt;Jin-woong Jo, Ye-ri Han, Hyeon-ju Son, Ahn Sung-Ki&lt;br /&gt;29 Jun 2016 (South Korea)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Korean Movie', 'Thriller', 'Lee Woo-Chul', 'Ahn Sung-Ki, Hyeon-ju Son, Jin-woong Jo, Ye-ri Han', 'South Korea', 'HDRip', '5.0', '1 jam 33 menit', '2016-06-29'),
(1750, 'The Huntsman: Winter&amp;#039;s War EXTENDED (2016)', '2017/07/film-huntsman-winters-war-2016.jpg', '', 'WGdxd1dFRHFYUUMvbjJRVjVwUmdaaEJSUG4wNXVFNHE1OEpaTFZBMy9FZz0=', '&lt;p&gt;As a war between rival queen sisters Ravenna and Freya escalates, Eric and fellow warrior Sara, members of the Huntsmen army raised to protect Freya, try to conceal their forbidden love as they combat Ravenna&amp;#8217;s wicked intentions.&lt;br /&gt;Cedric Nicolas-Troyan&lt;br /&gt;Chris Hemsworth, Charlize Theron, Jessica Chastain, Emily Blunt&lt;br /&gt;06 Apr 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Witch, Magic, Fairy Tale, Snow White, Huntsman', 'Action, Adventure, Drama', 'Cedric Nicolas-Troyan', 'Charlize Theron, Chris Hemsworth, Emily Blunt, Jessica Chastain', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.1', '2 jam 0 menit', '2016-04-06'),
(1751, 'The Inerasable (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-inerasable-2016.jpg', '', 'N2xPM2FKeFk4bTVxV2ZSSCtaZjVqQjlHaVdGV29MMDBldVFHUzZEMUhMOD0=', '&lt;p&gt;I is a successful writer of mystery-novels. One day she receives a letter from Kobu, a young student who recently moved into an apartment near her university. At night she hear strange noises and scary voices that got her afraid. She pleads I to help her. As a mystery-writer, I smells the ultimate story and decides to help Kobu. Together they uncover the truth about the people who lived in Kobu&amp;#8217;s apartment before. And it is a dark story full of anger, hatred, murder and suicide.&lt;br /&gt;Yoshihiro Nakamura&lt;br /&gt;Mansaku Fuwa, Ai Hashimoto, Ry&ocirc; Narita, Kentar&ocirc; Sakaguchi&lt;br /&gt;30 Jan 2016 (Japan)&lt;br /&gt;2 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Horror', 'Yoshihiro Nakamura', 'Ai Hashimoto, KentarÃƒÂ´ Sakaguchi, Mansaku Fuwa, RyÃƒÂ´ Narita', 'Japan', 'BluRay', '6.1', '1 jam 47 menit', '2016-01-30'),
(1752, 'The Innocents (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-innocents-2016.jpg', '', 'V09ZTHNQZ0laU1YvMzNkZnBjanBER3BRaDBvOVNyZlF1ZmZ3VzUxVER3Zz0=', '&lt;p&gt;In 1945 Poland, a young French Red Cross doctor who is sent to assist the survivors of the German camps discovers several nuns in advanced states of pregnancy during a visit to a nearby convent.&lt;br /&gt;Anne Fontaine&lt;br /&gt;Lou de La&acirc;ge, Agata Buzek, Agata Kulesza, Vincent Macaigne&lt;br /&gt;10 Feb 2016 (France, Poland)&lt;br /&gt;2 wins &amp;#038; 3 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Religion, Woman Director', 'Drama', 'Anne Fontaine', 'Agata Buzek, Agata Kulesza, Lou de LaÃƒÂ¢ge, Vincent Macaigne', 'France, Poland', 'BluRay', '7.4', '1 jam 55 menit', '2016-02-10'),
(1753, 'The Inhabitants (2015)', '', '', 'OFNMbFd3TFNYNUNTbU1WUlZkNTZHVENERnZWdVlQMEJKdU5PM3ZVWTlITT0=', '&lt;p&gt;A young couple gets more than they bargained for when they buy an historic bed and breakfast in New England only to discover that the old house is hiding a dark secret within its walls.&lt;br /&gt;Michael Rasmussen, Shawn Rasmussen&lt;br /&gt;Elise Couture, Michael Reed, India Pearl, Vasilios Asimakos&lt;br /&gt;13 Oct 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Haunted House, Bed And Breakfast Place, New England, Young Couple', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Michael Rasmussen, Shawn Rasmussen', 'Elise Couture, India Pearl, Michael Reed, Vasilios Asimakos', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '4.2', '1 jam 30 menit', '2015-10-13'),
(1754, 'The Institute (2017)', '2017/07/film-the-institute-2017.jpg', '', 'eW4rd0lyS1lBLzRKNTN5b0djNGtBV1JoaXFHdGMxbFo1dnJkOFJ1dzcxND0=', '&lt;p&gt;In 19th century Baltimore, a girl stricken with grief from her parents&amp;#8217; untimely death, voluntarily checks herself into the Rosewood Institute, and is subjected to bizarre and increasingly violent pseudo-scientific experiments in personality modification, brainwashing and mind control, she must escape the clutches of the Rosewood and exact her revenge.&lt;br /&gt;James Franco, Pamela Romanowsky&lt;br /&gt;Vincent Alvas, Pamela Anderson, Carmen Argenziano, Lauren B. Mosley&lt;br /&gt;03 Mar 2017 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Baltimore, 19th Century, Pseudo-scientific Experiments', 'Thriller', 'James Franco, Pamela Romanowsky', 'Carmen Argenziano, Lauren B. Mosley, Pamela Anderson, Vincent Alvas', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '4.0', '1 jam 30 menit', '2017-03-03'),
(1755, 'The Intent (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-intent-2016.jpg', '', 'SENOdExJc0VPQ29XZGJJVVJtYXp5ZHl6K1B4Q2xRdW5ldW5MUDZVYmp4VT0=', '&lt;p&gt;Gunz (Dylan Duffus) is thrust into a world of excitement when he joins the TIC crew. The crew, led by the ruthless Hoodz (Scorcher), goes from low level weed peddling to full on armed robberies within a fortnight. Their new found infamy affords them a life of guns, drugs, and girls but they also catch the attention of the police and a rival gang. To make matters worse they have been infiltrated by an undercover police officer. Does he have &amp;#8220;THE INTENT&amp;#8221; to remain a criminal or abide by his oath to the force?&lt;br /&gt;Femi Oyeniran, Kalvadour Peterson&lt;br /&gt;Dylan Duffus, Scorcher, Shone Romulus, Jade Asha&lt;br /&gt;29 Jul 2016 (UK)&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Crime, Drama', 'Femi Oyeniran, Kalvadour Peterson', 'Dylan Duffus, Jade Asha, Scorcher, Shone Romulus', 'Uk', 'HDRip', '3.5', '1 jam 44 menit', '2016-07-29'),
(1756, 'The Intern (2015)', '2017/07/film-the-intern-2015.jpg', '', 'UnFhWTZxZzBFb003RGxMMTdsL0ZVMHJVRnpNeGRESng1V01vclAvS1R0ST0=', '', '', 'Comedy', 'Nancy Meyers', 'Anders Holm, Anne Hathaway, Rene Russo, Robert De Niro', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '7.1', '2 jam 1 menit', '2015-09-25'),
