(1758, 'The Intervention (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-intervention-2016.jpg', '', 'dkNzL3dneldyb2tqYzllNEpJUWZTaHczRFNvNk5oNG1lbFJMQStCVDdTND0=', '&lt;p&gt;A weekend getaway for four couples takes a sharp turn when one of the couples discovers the entire trip was orchestrated to host an intervention on their marriage.&lt;br /&gt;Clea DuVall&lt;br /&gt;Natasha Lyonne, Alia Shawkat, Cobie Smulders, Clea DuVall&lt;br /&gt;26 Aug 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;1 win &amp;#038; 1 nomination.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Trip, Weekend, Marriage Crisis, Intervention, Directorial Debut, Getaway, Woman Director', 'Comedy, Drama', 'Clea DuVall', 'Alia Shawkat, Clea DuVall, Cobie Smulders, Natasha Lyonne', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.1', '1 jam 30 menit', '2016-08-26'),
(1759, 'The Invitation (2015)', '2017/07/film-the-invitation-2015.jpg', '', 'RERMS3l5bkFOSW0yUXV4YWFpTVhtdHhMaTdhR2lUeVhZRWdRZVlFam5MTT0=', '&lt;p&gt;Will and Eden were once a loving couple. After a tragedy took their son, Eden disappeared. Two years later, out of the blue, she returns with a new husband&amp;#8230; and as a different person, eerily changed and eager to reunite with her ex and those she left behind. Over the course of a dinner party in the house that was once his, the haunted Will is gripped by mounting evidence that Eden and her new friends have a mysterious and terrifying agenda. But can we trust Will&amp;#8217;s hold on reality? Or will he be the unwitting catalyst of the doom he senses?&lt;br /&gt;Karyn Kusama&lt;br /&gt;Logan Marshall-Green, Emayatzy Corinealdi, Aiden Lovekamp, Michelle Krusiec&lt;br /&gt;13 Mar 2015 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;3 wins &amp;#038; 1 nomination.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Psychological Thriller, Psycho Thriller, Reunited Friends, Dinner Party, Woman Director, Old Friends Reunited', 'Horror, Thriller', 'Karyn Kusama', 'Aiden Lovekamp, Emayatzy Corinealdi, Logan Marshall-Green, Michelle Krusiec', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.7', '1 jam 40 menit', '2015-03-13'),
