(1764, 'The King (2017)', '2017/07/film-the-king-2017.jpg', '', 'Ny9lNjRkYVRqNis3clRrUGZwVks1ajFLYWh4MTAveWsxbEZBclhtVEZscz0=', '&lt;p&gt;Park Tae Soo (Jo In Seong) terlahir dalam sebuah keluarga yang miskin. Ia memutuskan untuk menjadi seorang jaksa setelah ia menyadari jika kekuasaan merupakan salah satu hal yang terpenting dalam hidup. Setelah berhasil lulus dan menjadi seorang jaksa, dia merasa jika hidupnya tidak lebih hebat dari mereka yang menerima gaji setiap bulan. Karena itu ia mencoba untuk meraih kekuasaan yang lebih besar lagi dan terpaksa harus menghadapai segala sesuatu yang menghampirinya sebagai konsekuensi atas keserakahan dan ketamakannya&lt;br /&gt;Jae-rim Han&lt;br /&gt;In-seong Jo, Ryoo Joon-Yeol, Woo-sung Jung, Bae Sung-Woo&lt;br /&gt;18 Jan 2017 ()&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Crime, Drama', 'Jae-rim Han', 'Bae Sung-Woo, In-seong Jo, Ryoo Joon-Yeol, Woo-sung Jung', 'Korea', 'WEBDL', '7.0', '2 jam 14 menit', '2017-01-18'),
(1765, 'The Lady in the Car with Glasses and a Gun (2015)', '2017/07/film-the-lady-in-the-car-with-glasses-and-a-gun-2015.jpg', '', 'dEEvbG5nNnNjMEticVlaUllHTHJ3ZTNLcW91YTVmQnJIb2JVMC9mekl1QT0=', '&lt;p&gt;The trials and tribulations of Dany Dorm&eacute;us.&lt;br /&gt;Joann Sfar&lt;br /&gt;Freya Mavor, Benjamin Biolay, Elio Germano, Stacy Martin&lt;br /&gt;05 Aug 2015 (France, Belgium)&lt;br /&gt;1 win.&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Thriller', 'Joann Sfar', 'Benjamin Biolay, Elio Germano, Freya Mavor, Stacy Martin', 'Belgium, France', 'BluRay', '5.5', '1 jam 33 menit', '2015-08-05'),
(1766, 'The Land (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-land-2016.jpg', '', 'eTZ2WmxXRG4xaktNOW15YjE3KzFNdkxwc3RFR3hNYW5kc3FwV2VjeC9pND0=', '&lt;p&gt;THE LAND tells the story of four teenage boys who devote their summer to escaping the streets of Cleveland, Ohio to pursue a dream life of professional skateboarding. But when they get caught in the web of the local Queen-pin, their motley brotherhood is tested, threatening to make this summer their last.&lt;br /&gt;Steven Caple Jr.&lt;br /&gt;Jorge Lendeborg Jr., Moises Arias, Rafi Gavron, Ezri Walker&lt;br /&gt;29 Jul 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;1 win.&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Drama', 'Steven Caple Jr.', 'Ezri Walker, Jorge Lendeborg Jr., Moises Arias, Rafi Gavron', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '6.4', '1 jam 42 menit', '2016-07-29'),
(1767, 'The Lady in the Van (2015)', '2017/07/film-lady-van-2015.jpg', '', 'ZG41bUtXQnNVRHV5SC9KL3hxMDhtdHdnV2JBYlQ2SzJlNDE2SHFCc0cwOD0=', '&lt;p&gt;The Lady in the Van tells the true story of Alan Bennett&amp;#8217;s strained friendship with Miss Mary Shepherd, an eccentric homeless woman whom Bennett befriended in the 1970s before allowing her temporarily to park her Bedford van in the driveway of his Camden home. She stayed there for 15 years. As the story develops Bennett learns that Miss Shepherd is really Margaret Fairchild (died 1989), a former gifted pupil of the pianist Alfred Cortot. She had played Chopin in a promenade concert, tried to become a nun, was committed to an institution by her brother, escaped, had an accident when her van was hit by a motorcyclist for which she believed herself to blame, and thereafter lived in fear of arrest.&lt;br /&gt;Nicholas Hytner&lt;br /&gt;Maggie Smith, Jim Broadbent, Clare Hammond, George Fenton&lt;br /&gt;04 Dec 2015 (UK)&lt;br /&gt;Nominated for 1 Golden Globe. Another 1 win &amp;#038; 3 nominations.&lt;br /&gt;', 'Based On Novel, Biography, Based On True Story', 'Biography, Comedy, Drama', 'Nicholas Hytner', 'Clare Hammond, George Fenton, Jim Broadbent, Maggie Smith', 'Uk', 'BluRay', '6.7', '1 jam 44 menit', '2015-12-04'),
(1768, 'The Last Five Years (2015)', '2017/07/film-the-last-five-years-2015.jpg', '', 'VVlGbVBpK2RoY0xkZGJoaDI0UVRFNDZ1cEdUeklwNlFzSlNVWUVPeXhiQT0=', '', '', 'Comedy, Drama, Musical', 'Richard LaGravenese', 'Anna Kendrick, Cassandra Inman, Jeremy Jordan, Tamara Mintz', 'Usa', 'BluRay', '5.9', '1 jam 34 menit', '2015-02-13'),
(1769, 'The Last King (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-last-king-2016.jpg', '', 'K21ERzJibDJPWjkrNVB5ZlFPSTlKNmRqcC96TGFwUDlVMEpvaXNQODkrQT0=', '&lt;p&gt;In the year 1206 Norway is raged by civil war. The King&amp;#8217;s illegitimate infant son, H&aring;kon H&aring;konsson, which half the kingdom wants killed off, is guarded in secrecy by two men. A story which changed the course of the country&amp;#8217;s history.&lt;br /&gt;Nils Gaup&lt;br /&gt;Anders Dahlberg, &Aring;smund Brede Eike, Elg Elgesem, P&aring;l Sverre Hagen&lt;br /&gt;16 Feb 2016 (Norway)&lt;br /&gt;', 'Civil War, Norway', 'Action, Adventure, Drama', 'Nils Gaup', 'Anders Dahlberg, ÃƒÂ…smund Brede Eike, Elg Elgesem, PÃƒÂ¥l Sverre Hagen', 'Norway', 'BluRay', '6.1', '1 jam 39 menit', '2016-02-16'),
(1770, 'The Last Heist (2016)', '2017/07/film-the-last-heist-2016.jpg', '', 'Q05iOTkxNGkxUEg5RDdWblptYW9tTXd1UzlkVjYwcFRYdFVqemhGODRqdz0=', '&lt;p&gt;A bank heist descends into violent chaos when one of the hostages turns out to be a serial killer. Trapping the well-organized team of bank robbers in the building, the killer is now picking them off one by one.&lt;br /&gt;Mike Mendez&lt;br /&gt;Henry Rollins, Torrance Coombs, Victoria Pratt, Mykel Shannon Jenkins&lt;br /&gt;17 Jun 2016 (USA)&lt;br /&gt;', '', 'Action', 'Mike Mendez', 'Henry Rollins, Mykel Shannon Jenkins, Torrance Coombs, Victoria Pratt', 'Usa', 'HDRip', '3.5', '1 jam 40 menit', '2016-06-17'),
